019package com.plotsquared.core.location;
020
021import com.plotsquared.core.util.MathMan;
022import com.plotsquared.core.util.StringMan;
023
024public record ChunkWrapper(
025        String world,
026        int x,
027        int z
028) {
029
030    @Override
031    public int hashCode() {
032        return MathMan.pair((short) x, (short) z);
033    }
034
035    @Override
036    public boolean equals(Object obj) {
037        if (this == obj) {
038            return true;
039        }
040        if (obj == null) {
041            return false;
042        }
043        if (this.hashCode() != obj.hashCode()) {
044            return false;
045        }
046        if (getClass() != obj.getClass()) {
047            return false;
048        }
049        ChunkWrapper other = (ChunkWrapper) obj;
050        return (this.x == other.x) && (this.z == other.z) && StringMan
051                .isEqual(this.world, other.world);
052    }
053
054    @Override
055    public String toString() {
056        return this.world + ":" + this.x + "," + this.z;
057    }
058
059}
